## Notes

- Built for **personal learning** based on IWCF well-control kill-sheet methodology
- **Not intended** for official, certified, or commercial well-control operations
- PDF targets **A4 portrait**; value boxes match the paper IWCF Subsea form layout
- All calculations use **API field units** — ppg, psi, feet, barrels, bbl/ft
- Rounding follows IWCF convention: Max MW rounds **down**, KMW rounds **up**
- Choke line length and marine riser length entered in Section 2 are reused automatically
  in Section 4 — no double entry required
- No internet connection required; all data stays on-device

